{"tid":1211241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢啲唔叫革命，係「暴動」","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:25:39.000Z","uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e92bdc7b74ebe310de56a56e6ee4adc3368e0bb9","tid":1211241,"uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"自古以嚟革命成功嘅前題係雙方嘅武力水平要對等。冷兵器時代都仲可以攞農具去同官兵搏，現代人面對嘅係一大堆針對性嘅裝備，甚至係槍。<br />\n<br />\n現代革命真係好難會成功，由其係香港呢個地方。香港人由細到大接受嘅教育就係有事就去揾「警察叔叔」，基本上每一個小朋友都被灌輸過呢個觀念。久而久之就變左一群綿羊，就算係勇武派都唔會太激進。仲衍生咗一個警察都一樣係香港人的觀念，仲想感化佢地。<br />\n<br />\n所以，係武力嚴重懸殊嘅時候就應該退，而唔係一味叫人衝同支援，再多支援都無用。 雖然話蟻多可以摟死象，咁如果隻象係鋼做嘅呢？<br />\n我地同當權者嘅實力差距就係咁大，呢個係事實。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚再叫人出去<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再話咩係香港人就出去<br />\n<br />\n出去只係送死咋<br />\n<br />\n我唔想周圍嘅戰友越黎越少啊<br />\n<br />\n記住，命就得一條，唔好比熱血衝昏頭腦</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8d6c0cc394f1d47ed710b14e825ef767b0120be","tid":1211241,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係呀！大家返屋企，等條例通過好冇</span>"},{"pid":"795d06b4e7734d23e0b82a8370a5005c5a50933f","tid":1211241,"uid":25391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"口罩 水樽就話人暴動<br />\n講出去會唔會比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976767850b38f986812cf3362857d631ccf111fe","tid":1211241,"uid":10466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aV9EsRb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaV9EsRb.png&h=6d1573a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21f1d429b9f4131b895be69734a450dc2347164f","tid":1211241,"uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795d06b4e7734d23e0b82a8370a5005c5a50933f","tid":1211241,"uid":25391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"口罩 水樽就話人暴動<br />\n講出去會唔會比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"港共講係咩都得架啦<br />\n要記住佢哋係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共 產 黨</span></span>"}]}